msgid "[[!meta title=\"Chat\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Chat\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Join our XMPP chat room to ask questions about Tails."
msgstr "Únete a nuestro chat XMPP para preguntar sobre Tails."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To do so, you need an XMPP account. Some emails providers, such as [Riseup]"
"(https://help.riseup.net/en/chat), provide XMPP accounts as well."
msgstr ""
"Para hacerlo, necesitas una cuenta XMPP. Algunos proveedores de email, como "
"[Riseup](https://help.riseup.net/en/chat), dan cuentas de XMPP también."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Then configure your preferred instant messaging client, for example [[Pidgin|"
"http://www.pidgin.im/]], which runs on Windows, GNU/Linux, and macOS, to "
"connect to:"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, configura tu cliente de mensajería instantánea preferido, por "
"ejemplo  [[Pidgin|http://www.pidgin.im/]], que funciona en Windows, GNU/"
"Linux, y macOS, para conectar a:"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "server: `conference.riseup.net`"
msgstr "server: `conference.riseup.net`"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "room: `tails`"
msgstr "room: `tails`"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "Use TLS/SSL to connect!"
msgstr "¡Usa TLS/SSL para conectarte!"
